3 SUMMARY
44 This bill repeals provisions enacted by Public Law 2023, chapter 648 protecting
55 persons who seek, health care practitioners who provide and those who assist health care
66 practitioners in providing gender-affirming health care services and reproductive health
77 care services in accordance with the applicable standard of care. The bill replaces the
88 provisions addressed in chapter 648 with the law that was in effect prior to enactment of
99 chapter 648.
